snippet.title: Skald - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Here's your look at gameplay, including exploration, in this latest trailer for Skald: Against the Black Priory an upcoming retro-style RPG set in a grim-dark fantasy world of tragic heroes, violent deaths, and Lovecraftian horror. A demo for Skald is available now on Steam.
